Member Function Documentation

readNext ( $  a = array()  ) 

Read the next entity from the prepared file or string.

Invoke this after readString() or readFile().

Parameters:
$a Options.
Returns:
The return type and value is different for each class that overloads readNext() but all classes will return false when the next element cannot be read - because of an error or EOF.

Implemented in CMFileCSV, CMFileICAL, and CMFileVCF.
